README
------

Core scripts.
- build.ps1             build script.
- harness.cmd           plain test harness.
- test.ps1              test script.
- cover.ps1             code coverage script.
- pack.ps1              create a package.
- test-package.ps1      test a package.

Maintenance scripts.
- freeze-api.ps1        update public API files.
- reset.ps1             reset the repository.

Other files.
- asm.ps1               retrieve various assembly infos.
- utils.ps1             generic helpers.
- abc.ps1               project-specific helpers.
- NETFxTools            blank project used to restore .NET Framework tools.

Obsolete files.
- genuids.fsx           generate unique ids used to timestamp a package.
- genuids.ps1           execute genuids.fsx.
- Pack.tasks            MSBuild tasks when building packages.

Quick tests
-----------

Quickly run the test suite for the default target.
> dotnet test src\Abc.Tests
> dotnet test src\Abc.Tests -c Release /p:Retail=true

Filtering
> dotnet test --filter Category=XXXX
> dotnet test --filter Priority!=XXX -v q

Dump the test suite.
> dotnet test --list-tests
